narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Special resources were not required for this course. We used the fabrication lab to complete the column testing lab.
Since the course was mainly theorectical not many resources were needed. Those that were used to supplement the course were fun--like the crusher in the basement
The classroom is typically very cold.
